From fe3d3120c8cd2bb4a96430cc22cc658917d91d9d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Shingo <boomker@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Fri, 5 Jun 2026 18:38:24 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add insertSpaceBetweenChineseAndEnglish config option

Reorder BehaviorConfig fields to group related options
together, rename "Default Candidates per page" to "Default
maximum candidates per page", and add a new
insertSpaceBetweenChineseAndEnglish boolean option with
translations across all supported locales.
